data.description: ***PRICE REDUCTION*** Live in Sandy with an ADU that helps you pay for the mortgage! FHA assumable loan at the incredible rate of 2.7 % to a qualified buyer. This amazing corner property has a super-size/all-flat backyard. What are you going to do with all this land? there is room enough to store your RV and boat and still have space to enjoy your barbecues in the summer, entertain friends, build an extra shed, etc. The possibilities are endless! It also has convenient access to 7800 South. The kitchen has been updated and has new appliances. Some projects were started and seller cannot finish them, this is your chance to add your personal final touches! You will love the mother-in-law's apartment at the front with a separate entrance. Live in the back and rent the front! or use it to start building your investment portfolio. Google Fiber connected. Home sold "as is". The entertainment center drawers, fireplace, and TV will be included with a full price offer. Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from county records and old MLS.  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
